data.description: Lovely Pool home on big landscaped lot in Central Citrus County.  All 3 bedrooms have their own bath in this home! Perfect for an expanded family situation.  Large great room with high ceilings and a fireplace! Hugh lanai overlooking a 14 x 32 caged in pool and large back yard.  Easy access from the rear lane for your RV or boat!  Over a half acre lot with gorgeous oak trees, sprinkler system, workshop and lovely landscaping. No HOA here!  Easy access to East or West Citrus County for shopping, dining, hospitals and our amazing waterways.
